column5: To all, have a great and SAFE long weekend with family and  friends. We will have all of our kids and grands on Sunday (17 in all) noisy but great to have them, hei wait a minute they come every Sunday!  Be safe.  to all of our American cousins come on up and join us, we love you, there I go with tourism again
Happy Thanksgiving day to all of my Northern brothers and sisters. Enjoy and be safe.   Art
Should be a good one! New baby, my oldest boy, family, friends... Pumpkin picking, corn mazes and candy apples. Looking forward to this time together. I have a lot to be thankful for.  G
Like Jen says... it's pumpkin carving shootin time!!  Enjoy everyone !
